          Otherwise, if someone was holding a card upright, the other players
          would know he's holding not holding a letter (XAJQK) for sure.
        </p><h2 id="other-details" class="group flex -ml-[1rem]">
          <span class="not-prose w-[1rem] -mt-[0.125rem]">
            <a
